SEE THE MATTRESS







★★★★★See why our customers love their Loom & LeafREAD OUR REVIEWS > 

Ultra-luxury at a fraction of the price

Loom & Leaf is the luxury memory foam mattress by Saatva,
the company FORBES named to its top 100 companies to watch.

Objectively measured, Loom & Leaf  is best compared to iComfort and Tempur-Pedic®, 
but our efficient online business model allows us to charge significantly less. Many e-commerce 
sites offer memory foam beds that get rolled in a box and dropped on your doorstep. While our 
L&L mattress is priced slightly higher than these products, our quality is simply superior. Our delivery 
teams deliver and set up your mattress in the room of your choice, anywhere 
in the contiguous United States and parts of Canada.

Loom & Leaf is the smart, luxurious answer.





The perfect memory foam mattress







Our dense, 5 lb eco-friendly foam coupled with our multi-layered foam construction should never be crammed into a box. The L&L bed is delivered complete and set up in your home, with nationwide delivery.
        

Our breathable, organic cotton covering and natural thistle flame retardant keep you comfortable, cool and safe.
        

We use cooling gel to ensure you don’t overheat. Make every evening cool and comfortable. 
        

Loom & Leaf mattresses work with traditional and adjustable bases, allowing them to provide the perfect amount of comfort and support at every angle. 
        

Our American-made mattresses are 1/2 the price of a Tempur-Pedic®*,  making L&L the intelligent choice in premium memory foam. Our business model eliminates all brick and mortar mark-ups.
        
* $4,799 Queen TEMPUR-Cloud® Luxe Breeze at Tempurpedic.com® vs $1,099 Queen Loom & Leaf obtained 4/28/2017



