About our frames

The bed frame fits all sizes of bedding. The center rail has 3 heavy duty legs for maximum center support from head to toe. The center support can be used on all sizes for maximum stability and support. 

The frame has a total of 7 heavy duty legs with floor guides. The frame sits 7.5" off the ground.



Our mattress removal service

The fee of $39.00 includes the removal of up to two items from your home (mattress and foundation, two mattresses or two foundations).

If you have more than two items the charge is $19.50 per item starting with the third item. Please add your additional item to you order  here  or contact us directly at 1-877-762-2882.





About our foundations



8.75" Foundation



4.75" Foundation


Like those found in most of today's premium interactive mattress sets, we offer a rigid solid support foundation that utilizes a solid deck support with a wood slat construction for maximum mattress and body support. Additionally, the foundation contains our eco-friendly foams and is covered in organic cotton.
Our foundation is available in two thickness options — a standard 8.75" foundation and a 4.75" low-profile foundation. Both are available in twin, full, queen, king, and California king sizes. There is absolutely no difference in the feel between the low-profile 4.75" and the standard 8.75".
All king and Cal king size foundations come split for delivery purposes, as they do not bend. The split foundation will fit into any entranceway or doorway. Twin, full, and queen all come standard in one piece.
Please note that we do have a split queen foundation available for an additional $35.00. This should be ordered if you feel a standard queen one-piece foundation won't fit into your entranceway or doorway. That option is not available in full or twin.




We guarantee that your mattress is crafted fresh, to our strict specifications. All mattresses are thoroughly inspected before being sent out for delivery to your home.


