We make getting sleepy easy

All Loom & Leaf memory foam beds sleep cool, making for a very comfortable night's sleep. Choose from two comfort levels depending on your sleep preferences.
  




L&L Relaxed Firm
This is our flagship comfort level — not too hard, not too soft,  "just right" support.


L&L Firm
For customers who wanta very firm feel.


We do not recommend memory foam in this range because it becomes too "mushy," resulting in an unhealthy lack of support. 
  

    This range is too hard to support healthy sleep and joint comfort.
  



Ready to get a great night's sleep? Choose your comfort level.





Loom & Leaf Relaxed Firm

      This is our flagship comfort level — the "sweet spot" 
      between not too hard and not too soft.
      For our customers who like a just-right feel, or:
      If you prefer to sleep on your side, back or stomach 
      or you switch sleeping positions often in the night.
    

CHOOSE RELAXED FIRM







Loom & Leaf Firm

      For our customers who prefer a very firm feel, or:
      If you prefer to sleep on your back or stomach.
      If your health professional has recommended 
      a firmer mattress.
    

