1. 
Quilted, organic cotton covering

Our breathable, organic cotton covering and natural thistle flame retardant keep you comfortable, cool and safe.
    

2. 
Cooling spinal gel

Our proprietary Spinal Zone Gel layer is created with cooling gel so you stay cool with optimal spinal support.


3. 
Eco-friendly, 5lb premium foam



Our 5 lb eco-friendly premium top memory foam layer is naturally cool with no off-gassing. American-made L&L foams are delivered whole and stable.




4. 
Dual layer breathable support



Our dual layer eco-friendly support foam with breathable airflow channels provides a cool, supportive night’s sleep.









