We only use 5 lb foam sourced in the US.

This is a unique memory foam bed that isn’t your standard block of foam. We wanted to create a masterpiece — combining the luxurious features of a cool, contouring 5 lb memory foam with the ultra-luxury feel of our proprietary, multi-layered foams finished in our organic cotton quilt covering.
  

