      Published Jan 28, 2015 by Aaron












19,656 of 20,397 people found the following review helpful
No regrets!!
I was originally skeptical about making a mattress purchase online, however, after my experiences with Saatva…I am very happy that I took the chance.  I purchased my Saatva mattress in November 2014 and felt it necessary to wait until now before posting a review.  I chose to write this simply because I relied on others reviews to help me make my decision to purchase, and I hope it helps you if you are on the fence about making the plunge…so here you go.

I have had my mattress for a little over 60 days and I am in love.  The purchase was very simple and easy to complete online with no hidden fees throughout the process.  A few days after making my purchase I was sent an email containing details of my purchase and what to expect for delivery.

About 14 days after my purchase I received a phone call from the delivery company to set up a date and a time window for delivery.  The delivery company arrived when expected and was very professional.  The mattress and foundation were taken to an upstairs master bedroom and installed on my bed frame after they removed the old mattress and foundation.  I was worried about off gassing and chemical odors that are common with new mattresses and was quite surprised when this was not the case.

A few days after delivery, I did have a question about the foundation and subsequently sent Saatva an email.  Within 5 minutes of sending my email I received a phone call from Saatva with an answer to my question.  I have NEVER had a company respond so fast to an email and to do so with a phone call….simply amazing.  The Saatva representative was very responsive and nice, and she quickly answered my questions offering her direct number if anything comes up and I should have more questions.  I give Saatva’s customer service an A+.  This is reassuring to me that they stand behind their product and are willing to go above and beyond to make their customers feel like they made the right decision.    

So now about the mattress itself.  I purchased a king sized luxury firm and I gotta say that I have never had a better night’s sleep than I have had with my Saatva mattress.  I wake up feeling refreshed with absolutely no back pain.  Another thing I have noticed is that I dream more often which I believe means a more relaxing and deeper sleep.  

I feel comfortable recommending this mattress to anyone who is looking at replacing theirs.  Based on the quality of this mattress I am sure that it will last as long as Saatva claims, and even if there are problems, I am sure that Saatva’s awesome customer service will take great care of me.  If you are reading this wondering if you should take the chance on Saatva….do it….I did and have absolutely no regrets.                  
