TEMPUR-SEALY International
















Tempur-Sealy









Every day, thousands of consumers invite us into their home.





Tempur-Pedic®
Founded on innovation, delivering body-conforming support
From a history that includes NASA research and innovation by "Swedish scientists", came the original alternative mattress. Tempur® material uses body-conforming support and comfort to deliver your best night's sleep.








Tempur®
The global brand marketing body-conforming support to the world
With manufacturing facilities and offices across the globe, Tempur® brings body-conforming support and comfort to countries around the world.








Sealy®
The ideal blend of comfort and support, with an emphasis on value
Providing a better night's rest for over 130 years, Sealy® provides the ideal blend of comfort, support and value. Sealy® makes mattresses that people love, from a name they trust.








Sealy Posturepedic®
The comfort you want and the support you can trust for over 60 years
The most supportive mattress available from an American brand with heritage that goes back over 60 years. Sealy Posturepedic® is designed to support all of the living that happens in bed.








Optimum™ by Sealy Posturepedic
Helping to promote an optimum temperature range for a superior night's rest
Crafted with advanced OptiCool™ gel memory foam, Optimum™ gently cools to promote an optimum temperature range for deep, relaxing, restorative sleep. Great sleep is Optimum.








Stearns & Foster®
Bringing consumers luxurious materials and craftsmanship for over 167 years
Crafted from the highest quality materials from around the world, to produce one of the most luxurious mattresses on the market. Stearns & Foster® mattresses are made to stand the test of time.

























 



