We’ve transformed the 5-minute mattress test drive into a relaxing 120 day in home experience.

SHOP NOW








LEARN MORE

An honest approach, a customer-centric experience.

Did you know that nearly 20% of customers report that the bed they purchased and took home from a mattress store feels different than the one they tried at the store? Our 120 day home trial eliminates this nonsense. Our approach of having transparent policies coupled with extreme courtesy cuts through the traditional friction that is so common between mattress companies and consumers. We have very few returns, but if you find yourself in that position, know we will do everything in our power to make it smooth.
  




No penalty fees  /  No pick-up fees + We never restock
You are only responsible for the original delivery fee. Absolutely no other fees.We never restock a mattress.







120 day, no-penalty, 
home trial
      

We offer the friendliest home trial in the business: if you're not happy, you have the option to return our bed and only be responsible for the original delivery charge without penalty fees or restocking fees. Simply a refund. If you ordered the wrong item, we will offer a courtesy exchange for just the cost of delivery. 
      



Our qualityguarantee
      

We're confident your expectations will be exceeded from the day of delivery and beyond as our product continues to perform for you. By educating our customers on the benefits of our ultra premium bed with objective measures of comparison, we have had great success without ever having to use high pressure or confusing tactics. 
      



