Built for luxury comfort and maximum sustainability.
Handcrafted & American Made
          To match the specs and materials of our queen mattress, which is compatible with an adjustable base, retail stores charge $2,749*. Our price, just $999.
* Simmons Beautyrest Black Hybrid Gladney 14" Luxury Firm Mattress at Mattress Firm
Choose comfort level 














Saatva mattresses are built with a distinctive high quality feature known as 'coil on coil' construction. Our lower coil unit offers a connected hourglass shaped steel support base. Our top coil unit features a luxurious individually wrapped coil system that contours and responds perfectly to your body, eliminating most motion transfer. Each individually wrapped coil is separate to ensure that the rest of the bed will not be disturbed by the movement of surrounding coils. This construction coupled with our advanced euro pillow top, can only be found in ultra premium mattresses that cost over $2,000 for a queen mattress. Our beds, which work with adjustable bases, are made to last 10 to 15 years and will continue to perform consistently well over time.  Note: All Saatva coil units are tempered three times and oven baked.SEE COMFORT LEVELS


We have uniquely combined the top 5 features found in ultra premium bedding and handcrafted them into one perfect and affordable luxury mattress.
Our standard premier luxury mattress is 14.5". We also make a custom slim 11.5" that was redesigned in March 2017 to work with adjustable bases, including the Lineal™ Adjustable Base by Saatva. The quality and feel of the mattresses are the same.







1
Individually Wrapped Comfort Coils

Individually wrapped coils in the top portion of the mattress are the most advanced coil system in the luxury mattress market. These coils respond and contour to every body shape.

  


2
Dual Perimeter Edge Support System


Foam encased anti-sag edge support for better durability and more sleep surface. The Saatva Mattress uses a Dual Perimeter Edge Support System. The upper comfort coils are foam encased.  This is a quality that only the most durable and best mattresses have.

  


3
Lumbar Support Enhancement


Lumbar support enhancement made of high quality memory foam layer, providing additional pressure relief while helping reduce stress and tension from the lower back.

  


4
Steel Coil Base Support System


All Saatva’s luxury mattresses are built with a tempered steel support lower coil base. This creates a long lasting, sustainable mattress with increased durability and is the best design to prevent sagging. 

  


5
Organic Cotton Cover & Euro Pillow Top


The euro pillow top offers more padding and cushioning materials than what is found in most regular pillow tops. These materials are then inserted underneath the outer covering for a neater and cleaner look. Regular pillow tops that are sewn to the top of a bed tend to shift and lose shape.

  



Choose Your
Comfort Level








































